<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>ChaseSystem</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Processes<sp/>entities<sp/>with<sp/>`ChaseComponent`,<sp/>`SteeringComponent`,<sp/>and<sp/>`TranslationStateComponent`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>Behavior</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">1.<sp/>**Target<sp/>Resolution**:<sp/>Looks<sp/>up<sp/>target<sp/>entity<sp/>by<sp/>handle</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">2.<sp/>**Timer<sp/>Update**:<sp/>Advances<sp/>cooldown<sp/>timer<sp/>by<sp/>delta<sp/>time</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">3.<sp/>**Cooldown<sp/>Check**:<sp/>Only<sp/>updates<sp/>direction<sp/>when<sp/>timer<sp/>exceeds<sp/>cooldown</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">4.<sp/>**Direction<sp/>Calculation**:<sp/>Computes<sp/>normalized<sp/>vector<sp/>from<sp/>entity<sp/>to<sp/>target</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">5.<sp/>**Steering<sp/>Update**:<sp/>Sets<sp/>steering<sp/>intent<sp/>to<sp/>face<sp/>calculated<sp/>direction</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">###<sp/>Required<sp/>Components</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>Component<sp/>|<sp/>Purpose<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|-----------|---------|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>`ChaseComponent`<sp/>|<sp/>Target<sp/>handle<sp/>and<sp/>timing<sp/>configuration<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>`SteeringComponent`<sp/>|<sp/>Receives<sp/>steering<sp/>intent<sp/>updates<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>`TranslationStateComponent`<sp/>|<sp/>Provides<sp/>current<sp/>entity<sp/>position<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
